    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of the arthropod group that includes spiders, daddy longlegs, scorpions, and (in the subclass Acari) the mites and ticks, as well as lesser-known subgroups.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
